Sentencas: Multi-layered (Y2O3)(0.08)(ZrO2)(0.92)/(Sc2O3)(0.1)(CeO2)(0.01)-(ZrO2)(0.89)(YSZ/SCSZ) electrolytes have been designed, so that the inner SCSZ layers provided superior ionic conductivity and the outer YSZ skin layers maintained good chemical and phase stability.
Titulo: Residual Stress and Biaxial Strength in Sc2O3-CeO2-ZrO2/Y2O3-ZrO2 Layered Electrolytes

Sentencas: Due to the mismatch of coefficients of thermal expansion between layers of different compositions, the thermal residual stresses were generated.
Titulo: Residual Stress and Biaxial Strength in Sc2O3-CeO2-ZrO2/Y2O3-ZrO2 Layered Electrolytes

Sentencas: The theoretical residual stress and strain were calculated for different thickness ratios of the electrolytes.
Titulo: Residual Stress and Biaxial Strength in Sc2O3-CeO2-ZrO2/Y2O3-ZrO2 Layered Electrolytes

Sentencas: In order to study the residual stress effect on the mechanical properties, the biaxial flexure tests of electrolytes with various layered designs were performed via a ring-on-ring method at room temperature and 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Residual Stress and Biaxial Strength in Sc2O3-CeO2-ZrO2/Y2O3-ZrO2 Layered Electrolytes

Sentencas: The maximum principal stress at the fracture indicated improved flexure strength in the electrolytes with layered designs at both temperatures.
Titulo: Residual Stress and Biaxial Strength in Sc2O3-CeO2-ZrO2/Y2O3-ZrO2 Layered Electrolytes

Sentencas: It is believed to be the result of the residual compressive stress in the outer YSZ layer.
Titulo: Residual Stress and Biaxial Strength in Sc2O3-CeO2-ZrO2/Y2O3-ZrO2 Layered Electrolytes

Sentencas: In addition, the Weibull statistics of the stress at the fracture at room temperature was studied, and the values of residual stress presented at the outer layer were well verified.
Titulo: Residual Stress and Biaxial Strength in Sc2O3-CeO2-ZrO2/Y2O3-ZrO2 Layered Electrolytes
